parser:
.TP
.B \-\-dtdload
Load the external DTD.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \-\-huge
Remove any internal arbitrary parser limits.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \-\-net
Allow network access to load external DTD and entities.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \-\-noent
Resolve entities.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \-\-xinclude
Do XInclude processing.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \-\-xml\-catalog <file>
Use an XML catalog when resolving entities.
